<h1>Dashboard</h1>
<br />
<p>
The Dashboard is a quick way to access a patient that is checked into a specific location.
</p>
<br />
<h2>
1. Click on the 'Dashboard' button.<br />
<img src="/images/Dashboard1.PNG" alt="Dashboard image 1" width="99%" />
<br />
<br />
2. Click on the Drop-Down arrow of the 'Select Location' box.<br />
<img src="/images/Dashboard2.PNG" alt="Dashboard image 2" width="99%" />
<br />
<br />
3. Select a location from the list.<br />
<img src="/images/Dashboard3.PNG" alt="Dashboard image 3" width="99%" />
<br />
<br />
4. Click the 'Show Checkins' button.<br />
<img src="/images/Dashboard4.PNG" alt="Dashboard image 4" width="99%" />
<br />
<br />
5. The patients checked into that location will be listed below.<br />
<img src="/images/Dashboard5.PNG" alt="Dashboard image 5" width="99%" />
6. Click on the row containing the desired patient to be taken directly to that patient's information.<br />
</h2>
<br />
